                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Choate</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-02-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 13, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Choate reports that Lord Lansdowne has informed him that the British
                    representatives at St. Petersburg, Tokyo, and Peking have been instructed to
                    present the request for the neutrality of China on the lines laid down in the
                    memorandum of the 11th instant.)</p>
            </div>
